se.kth.ict.docaid.course

Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.kth.ict.docaid.course.Course

  • public class Course
extends java.lang.Object
    The class holds information about a course. It contains all information extracted from the XML web page of the course, along with an instance of the class reader. The reader contains extracted keywords, keyphrases and abbreviations from the hope page of the course.
    Author:
    andrew
